{"tid":1649972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經過今日 popo分化策略已進化","createTime":"2019-10-12T19:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T19:33:10.000Z","uid":31055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"55b75fc6175449994ed419f6cbe8926c2ee643c4","tid":1649972,"uid":31055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:17:24.000Z","msg":"生日蛋糕果班豬隊友屌完就算 <br />\n俾Popo發現我地原來因為一個蛋糕又起底又報驚 <br />\n分化容乜易 以後一於派十幾廿隻狗落去<br />\n打牌打邊爐食蛋糕唱K<br />\n一有人開拖就影撚哂上電視報紙<br />\n再出師有名派防暴係人都9拉 <br />\n話俾班藍屍知我地幾咁易散 場運動變左質<br />\n<br />\n以後一有on9仔開P 一撚定係鬼係分化撚 <br />\n唔撚洗同佢地嘈 唔使獅鳥<br />\n幾個手足大嗌 五大訴求 缺一不可！ 我哋唔係來玩！<br />\n嗌撚到佢地喱番入狗竇<br />\n<br />\n成大事必要具大氣 一個蛋糕唔會分化到我地 <br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"cc3af9210bd8c32512b832376a73825681d864bf","tid":1649972,"uid":272292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:18:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26ce6ce0314bc0cfb94583faa4aa9c6109ef9159","tid":1649972,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:33:10.000Z","msg":"不篤灰 不割蓆唔係口號<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bMrUgfE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbMrUgfE.jpg&h=7e0b4b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n8OfK8Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn8OfK8Z.jpg&h=8241555a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Gc0WfF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Gc0WfF.png&h=b642bb0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XmEywO1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXmEywO1.png&h=04d87e0f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PEJvy2m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPEJvy2m.jpg&h=5fa169b0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}